These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, writing
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, october
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: daisy, begonia
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: superhero, martial-arts
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | writing       | traveling |
| Birthday         | october | november  |
| Flower       | begonia    | daisy    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts       | superhero      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: hiking, photography
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: rock, classical
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, february
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
2. the fan of rock is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Hobby      | photography     | hiking |
| Music-Genre           | rock | classical      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Birthday         | august | february     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
2 different games are played: whist, snooker
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: amaryllis, lily
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: ambient, country
House: farmhouse, cape-cod
1. the fan of country is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
2. the person playing whist is the cape-cod house##1
3. the person who growsamaryllis is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Game      | whist | snooker  |
| Flower          | amaryllis    | lily   |
| Music-Genre   | country  | ambient   |
| House     | cape-cod     | farmhouse |

