.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
City: rome, nizza
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, baccarat
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, may
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: punk, techno
1. the fan of punk is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
3. the person traveling to nizza is the dunhill-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| City      | rome       | nizza |
| Cigar          | baccarat         | dunhill    |
| Birthday           | may | october    |
| Music-Genre   | punk           | techno   |

