There 2 different types of food: cucumber, spinach
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, roller
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: jazz, ambient
1. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person eating cucumber##1
2. the person eating spinach is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the fan of ambient is on the left of the person driving the roller##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2     |
| Pet   | turtle         | snake    |
| Food       | spinach     | cucumber  |
| Transport      | tram | roller     |
| Music-Genre        | ambient     | jazz |

