.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
There are 2 different nationalities: russian, australian
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: crime, superhero
There are 2 different favourite colors: grey, orange
The people have 2 different hobbies: baking, cooking
1. the russian is on the right of the person watching crime movies##1
2. the russian is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the person who likes grey is the australian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Nationality           | australian | russian     |
| Movie-Genre   | crime          | superhero |
| Color           | grey          | orange    |
| Hobby     | cooking            | baking       |

 